
Description : No error is displayed when message field is left empty.
Severity - High
Priority - High
Assignee - Developer's Name
Summary : Application does not show any error when user attemps to submit the form without filling up Message field.
Steps to Reproduce:-
 1. Navigate to https://www.tendable.com/
 2. Click on Book a Demo.
 3. Click on Contact us here for support.
 4. Fill up Email, First Name, Last Name, Company Name, Leave Message Empty , Select Marketing as Message Type and select the check box.
 5. Click on Submit and verify if error message is displayed.

Expected Result : Error message 'Form Submission Failed' should be displayed.
Actual Result : Error message is not displayed.
